descriptionHtml:
My racemenu preset. You will need to extract the mod, and do the following with the .jslot file.

Install in Steamapps > Common > Skyrim > Mod Organizer > Overwrite > skse > Plugins > Chargen > Presets
OR Steamapps > Common > Skyrim > Data > SKSE > Plugins > Chargen > Plugins
[left][b]ONLY ONE OF THE ABOVE WILL WORK.[/b][/left][center][/center]To look exactly like the images, you will need the following:
